      • buildResourceURLListFromTemplate

        void buildResourceURLListFromTemplate(WMTSStatus status)
        If the layer has a template to build the URL, this method checks whether the format requested needs a template. If the template is needed the entire URL will be returned.
        Parameters:
        defaultDimension. - If this parameter is null, the default dimension will be used Parameters needed
        • Image format: Format to check if supports templates
        • Style identifier: Format to check if supports templates
        • Dimension: Parameter to build the URL replacing the dimension label
        • Tilematrixset: Parameter to build the URL replacing {TileMatrixSet}
        • tilematrix: Parameter to build the URL replacing {TileMatrix}
        • Tilerow: Parameter to build the URL replacing {TileRow}
        • Tilecol: Parameter to build the URL replacing {TileCol}
